Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Not that way, Ed! Turn left!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:11.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Al?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:12.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Just look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:15.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:17.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:33.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:50.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:53.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,So, what do you want me to do with...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:57.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:01:00.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Please, stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:07.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:11.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,We weren't hallucinating, were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:15.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,No, it was just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:18.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,We weren't hallucinating, were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:21.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,No, it was the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:24.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,I've got the proof right here in my hand.
